# ML checkpoints — too large for git (~200MB each, 1.2GB total).
# Download separately and mount via docker-compose volume.
# See docs/ENSEMBLE_NOTES.md for artifact sources.
models/*.ckpt
models/old_backup_*/

# Internal working docs — not for public repo
CLAUDE.md
PROMPTS.md

# Model artifacts — IP-sensitive; fetch separately when provisioning.
# .ckpt already excluded above. Pickles + training config + reference
# notebooks stay out of the repo. Tiny runtime-required text files
# (ticker lists, blocklist) are kept so fresh clones can boot services.
models/*.pkl
models/config.json
models/*.ipynb
